{"tid":1057004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港區人大代表王敏剛逝世終年70歲","createTime":"2019-03-11T14:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T01:11:59.000Z","uid":70063,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a52bdd6fcc1f0de62378894c7b479e832e725755","tid":1057004,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"全國港區人大代表王敏剛逝世，終年70歲。<br />\n<br />\n王敏剛的弟弟王敏超接受本台查詢時表示，王敏剛傍晚時份在瑪麗醫院因病離世，家人陪伴在側。<br />\n<br />\n王敏剛本月2日隨團抵達北京出席兩會會議，但因為身體不適，隨即進入北京醫院治療，本月4日在家人陪同下，回港接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1447183-20190311.htm?fbclid=IwAR1yPQT6aCsIm-DsQYugiiORUntSSQ2o3K4mRdw64I_KL_DFPdxsqf52Es4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1447183-20190311.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1yPQT6aCsIm-DsQYugiiORUntSSQ2o3K4mRdw64I_KL_DFPdxsqf52Es4&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6HWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=95a79e6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1447183-20190311.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1yPQT6aCsIm-DsQYugiiORUntSSQ2o3K4mRdw64I_KL_DFPdxsqf52Es4&h=f7a9f2de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1447183-20190311.htm?fbclid=IwAR1yPQT6aCsIm-DsQYugiiORUntSSQ2o3K4mRdw64I_KL_DFPdxsqf52Es4</a>"},{"pid":"71d136ce13bc23bafba4b4017455ee03bdf6e71f","tid":1057004,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e60ff610aa510056e16f8c27639ae9b947fde7","tid":1057004,"uid":35221,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"獲毛主席召見"},{"pid":"14ba532d41b332a59dcc16e660f51dc72d15582a","tid":1057004,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43d52083d71906d6ea5a7ba1359d66635099e3