oji\" />"},{"pid":"76cae7c0e4803772e1c616f05e5cdd37f94fa03f","tid":1057004,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777fd01871f5bdc822a580257b8ef89cd638626b","tid":1057004,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e60ff610aa510056e16f8c27639ae9b947fde7","tid":1057004,"uid":35221,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"獲毛主席召見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"玻璃棺材？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"玻璃棺要仆街到好似毛主席、列寧呢啲先瞓得"},{"pid":"96d86a6cd006036343fc9ab37a1aba0b97218267","tid":1057004,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"前排先報佢欠人好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url]http://（剛需代表）人大代表王敏剛借款1.55億買樓[/url] <a href=\"https://lih.kg/874024\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/874024</a>"},{"pid":"00177c19e41cee3206579674cc462e2beb500a15","tid":1057004,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"（剛需代表）人大代表王敏剛借款1.55億買樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/874024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/874024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"580fcaa0f69357fe4f8b6f0dd841c2ddfdd17c88","tid":1057004,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a653c85a42d69e61a4478720b0fd88c9a840ffca","tid":1057004,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"主營借貸及投資的新鴻基公司（086）發公告，指旗下新鴻基信貸與獨董王敏剛訂立貸款協議，新鴻基借出三筆貸款，首筆貸款額為1000萬元短期貸，期限6個月，年息18厘，通告指當中一半是用於「深水灣之住宅物業」購買價的按金及部分付款，另一半用於繳印花稅。<br />\n<br />\n第二筆貸款1.15億，為期1年，「使用於結算該物業購買價之餘額」，利率第一期為每年19.625%；第二至第十二期為每年7.625%。<br />\n<br />\n第三筆貸款3000萬元，利率每年7.625%，用於償還第一筆貸款及其業務之營運資金。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，王敏剛於2016年被海外註冊公司入稟高等法院申請破產。"},{"pid":"f4c02b5da1ecb61b3504dd8fa00ec56958c52d97","tid":1057004,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾多次要求23條立法的港區人代王敏剛亦稱，現時沒有立法迫切性，認為特區政府已成功運用《社團條例》打擊港獨。港區人代田北辰亦認為，現階段非合適時機討論23條立法。"},{"pid":"10680f9ef4d7e3c695af44c52e8fd911cfa6dcc8","tid":1057004,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T21:11:37.000Z","msg":"蒙毛寵召<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be08e31417dbc082533514cc219d18b4fcc1e41","tid":1057004,"uid":177955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T21:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但因為身體不適，隨即進入北京醫院治療，本月4日在家人陪同下，回港接受治療。</blockquote><br />\n北京醫院唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f445b30e2235d327bcf3b2e305287dd806ec0e","tid":1057004,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T21:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e119d3e404d37a5e21d6ec359ae2143e271c8337","tid":1057004,"uid":228360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T00:40:21.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e04915b8681de33ecf9345b2b3f1dee9fd42f3","tid":1057004,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4be08e31417dbc082533514cc219d18b4fcc1e41","tid":1057004,"uid":177955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T21:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但因為身體不適，隨即進入北京醫院治療，本月4日在家人陪同下，回港接受治療。</blockquote><br />\n北京醫院唔好？<img s